IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.linehaulleadtimereport') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.linehaulleadtimereport
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.linehaulleadtimereport (

[tripid] bigint,
[thirdpartyid] bigint,
[thirdpartyname] nvarchar(4000),
[bookingids] nvarchar(4000),
[loadids] nvarchar(4000),
[noofparcels] bigint,
[weight] float,
[chargeweight] numeric(36,6),
[volweight] float,
[volumiserweight] numeric(36,6),
[closeloadtostartdispatch] bigint,
[closeloadtoexitgeofence] bigint,
[effectiveloaddurationminutes] bigint,
[effectiveoffloaddurationminutes] bigint,
	)

	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/RPT/linehaulleadtimereport.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.linehaulleadtimereport
GO
